{"about_the_game":"Escape Abstraction reveals 7 abstract art paintings from the 1930s, reinterpreted in a 3D space. Enter the paintings, and you will find distorted, displaced shapes. You will have to interact with them to restore their original states. During your travel you will listen to a soothing soundtrack to accompany you on these minimalistic but challenging puzzles.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\nEach painting has an exit point that you will need to reach by moving on the shapes and interacting with them. Restoring the painting to its original state is optional but will impact your score!<br />\r\n<br />\r\nYou will be able to unlock new paintings throughout your adventure by discovering previous ones.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nPay close attention to the museum and you will find that it comes back to life as you piece together the paintings!<br />\r\n<br />\r\nWill you be able to restore each one of them?","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Klint Svanen","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1580850/a36e69848e3145faf5797627cf676397ca7017d2.jpg"},{"name":"Delaunay Rythmes","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1580850/f244df1c6d473c11aa366813c41208020b32c84d.jpg"},{"name":"Malevitch Suprematism","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1580850/59532a46344bcfad170f553470100484fe9c640d.jpg"},{"name":"Kandinsky Black Relationship","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1580850/581fc76a7f47ef85de89540172ae7c073e2c44b2.jpg"},{"name":"Klee The Messenger of Autumn","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1580850/b387abff356ed4e32a62ee00b5a167a8dee22532.jpg"},{"name":"Van Doesburg Composition in Grey","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1580850/f396e617abc364e269e773ff3159b3af746b4e96.jpg"},{"name":"Mondrian Victory Boogie Woogie","path":"https